Class TransformEdit

      org.jhotdraw.draw.event.TransformEdit
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.undo.UndoableEdit
public class TransformEdit
extends javax.swing.undo.AbstractUndoableEdit

An UndoableEdit event which can undo a lossless transform of Figures by applying the inverse of the transform to the figures.

This object is useful for undoing lossless transformations, such as the translation of figures.

If a lossy transforms is performed, such as rotation, scaling or shearing, then undos should be performed with TransformRestoreEdit instead.
